description: Clark & Amber fell in love with fresh hot fried fish while living by the beaches of Galveston. After moving back to the Bayou City and having zero luck finding restaurants serving fish that was quite as delicious, this cool couple took on the challenge themselves. After extensive preparation, Captain Clark’s Food Truck has hit the streets of Houston and is slinging out an incredibly tasty selection of Fish n’ Chips (with Texas-true Lone Star Beer-Battered Cod), Shrimp n’ Chips (with the perfect Panko crunch), and more. Whether you’re craving something amazing for your next meal or your next big event, Captain Clark’s Food Truck has got exactly what you need.
name: Captain Clark's Food Truck
